text: Hundstrup is a small town located on the island of Funen in south-central Denmark, in Svendborg Municipality. It is four kilometers north of Vester Skerninge and 14 kilometers northwest of Svendborg. The apple variety, Filippa originated in Hundstrup. == References == Category:Cities and towns in the Region of Southern Denmark Category:Svendborg Municipality
title: Hundstrup
